CustomField.description: Organizes firms into their supply chains. The full supply chain includes all elements of the generation of products and services including resource extraction through to the final delivery/installation and can include ongoing maintenance and operations. This allows the Salesforce owner of the account to identify if the account (organization) is in a supply chain of a specific segment of the sectors. Its helps to identify synergies and where there may be opportunities to support growth.
